vity of searches for GWs from binary\nblack holes in the advanced detector era.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Jan 2015 08:34:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 19 Jun 2015 02:45:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-24"}
